{"type": "article", "id": 13989, "title": "弹簧剪刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-26T07:49:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000258YhuO3pLcHZDJlFT4.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款来自荷兰阿姆斯特丹的 “80后” 设计师 Lex Pott 的弹簧剪刀。剪刀设计灵感来自传统的东方手工艺，弹簧钢的应用使得使用完成后剪刀可以自行恢复原状，这款剪刀左右手都适用，而其简单的设计和精巧的形状让它看起来像是一个艺术品。这是<a href=\"http://www.lexpott.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">Lex Pott 的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看他更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141628W07jxS2mzThGKNcX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6405959\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141628RCceOwtMVE1mAdWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141629kWOPFGU0HsJlz7NS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141630Rc5wbWsQaFvB4UjJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141630HgLaWTYENGAuOwCQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24791667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141631gdvakFewA520GJUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.28333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141632WVEQjISe1FdHOLcP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39479167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}